  "content": "HomeDirectorySuffolkSuffolk CountyPolice Station Representatives in SuffolkFind accredited police station representatives covering all Suffolk Constabulary custody suites. Available 24/7 for immediate attendance at Ipswich, Bury St Edmunds, Lowestoft and across Suffolk.Search Suffolk RepsRegister as Suffolk Rep1+Registered Suffolk Representatives14+Suffolk Police Stations24/7Coverage AvailablePolice Station Representation in SuffolkSuffolk is a scenic county in East Anglia, with Suffolk Constabulary operating custody suites at Martlesham (Ipswich), Bury St Edmunds, and Lowestoft. Our directory connects you with experienced, accredited professionals.All representatives listed hold current PSRAS accreditation through the Law Society.Suffolk Police Stations with Custody FacilitiesMartlesham Police Investigation Centre (Ipswich)Suffolk ConstabularyBury St Edmunds Police StationSuffolk ConstabularyLowestoft Police StationSuffolk ConstabularySudbury Police StationSuffolk ConstabularyView All Suffolk Stations Suffolk Police Station RepresentativesNishan EmmamdeenAccredited RepresentativeShow Contact Details•••• •••••••SuffolkStations Covered (2):Suffolk HeadquartersBury St Edmunds Police StationAvailability: All hoursAre You a Police Station Representative in Suffolk?Join our directory for free and get discovered by criminal defence firms across the county.Register for Free Become Featured",
